sketch.compiler.controlflow

Class StatementCounter

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.controlflow.DataFlow
      • sketch.compiler.controlflow.StatementCounter

  • public abstract class StatementCounter
extends DataFlow
    Data-flow analysis to count the number of times some qualifying statement appears in a CFG. Lattice values are CountLattice.

    $Id$

      • flowFunction

        public Lattice flowFunction(CFGNode node,
                            Lattice in)
        Modify a lattice value by passing through a CFG node. We're only particularly interested in statement nodes; if the statement at a statement node qualifies (as per statementQualifies(sketch.compiler.ast.core.stmts.Statement)), and the input value is a valued lattice value, the output is a lattice value for one more statement; otherwise, the output is the same as the input.
        Specified by:
        flowFunction in class DataFlow
        Parameters:
        node - CFG node to consider
        in - lattice value at entry to the node
        Returns:
        lattice value at exit from the node

        Determine if a statement should be counted.
        Returns:
        true if the statement should be counted
